parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature brake wear and failure can lead to reduced stopping power, increased stopping distances, and a higher risk of accidents, posing a significant safety risk to drivers and passengers.
symptoms: Grinding or squeaking sounds from the brakes
brake pads wearing out excessively
rotors needing to be replaced frequently
reduced braking performance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning hill hold feature can cause the vehicle to stall or roll back on hills, increasing the risk of accidents, especially when merging into traffic.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or rolls back on hills
the electronic parking brake engages unexpectedly
the hill hold feature takes too long to release the brakes
causing the vehicle to stall or lose momentum.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden opening of the passenger door while driving can cause a loss of control, accidents, or injuries to occupants.
symptoms: The passenger door opens unexpectedly while driving
no warning or indication is provided before the door opens
the door latch fails to engage properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the OCU Module can prevent emergency services from being contacted in the event of an accident, putting occupants at risk.
symptoms: The OCU Module fails to function
the cruise control malfunctions
the front assistance sensor does not work as intended
911 services are unavailable.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Remote App and SOS Emergency Call Function Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the remote app and SOS emergency call function can prevent emergency services from being contacted in the event of an accident, putting occupants at risk.
symptoms: The remote app functions stop working
a "SOS Error: Emergency Call Function! Service Vehicle!" warning appears on the dashboard
the error message persists
Bluetooth connectivity is lost
post-crash and SOS emergency calling are disabled.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the navigation system can cause distraction to the driver, leading to potential accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The navigation system stops working completely or works imprecisely
making it difficult for the driver to locate themselves.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Clutch Failure and Emergency Brake Issue
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and emergency brake can cause the vehicle to become stranded, leaving the driver in a potentially dangerous situation.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly stops moving
the clutch is burned out
the emergency brake is engaged despite not being activated by the driver.
